WEBVTT

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:04.500
Architect prompt: Design the architecture for the feedback widget.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:08.500
AgentX evaluates three architecture options.

00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:30.000
Option A: REST API with Postgres. Option B: Serverless with DynamoDB streams. Option C: Edge functions with key value store.

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:48.000
Decision: Option B. Consequences and a sequence diagram are recorded in the Tech Spec.

00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:53.500
ADR and Spec ready in one minute and four seconds. Three options scored. Zero code examples in spec.

00:00:54.000 --> 00:01:00.000
From prompt to defensible architecture. Powered by architect dot agent dot m d.
